caption: A heavy stack of metal cubes, consisting of a gold cube on top, two black cubes in the middle, and a silver cube at the base, stands precariously on a polished wooden floor. Suddenly, the stack begins to wobble, the cubes teetering. The gold cube at the top shifts slightly, causing the entire stack to lose balance. In a slow, almost graceful motion, the cubes tumble over, clattering onto the floor with a metallic clang. The gold cube rolls a short distance away, while the black and silver cubes scatter in different directions, coming to rest on the smooth surface.
